    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n7364" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πείρω</span></b> , ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔπειρον, πει&lt;&gt;͂ρε</span>, pass. perf.
          part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πεπαρμένος</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πέπαρτο</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">pierce through, pierce,
            transfix</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 16.405</span></i>; of
          piercing meat with spits (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κρέα
            ὀβελοῖσιν</span>), and pass., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἥλοισι
            πεπαρμένος</span>, ‘studded,’ <i><span class="en">Il.
            1.246</span></i>; fig., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀδύνῃσι</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 5.399</span></i>; also fig., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κέλευθον, κύ̄ματα</span>, ‘cleave’ one's way, ‘plow’
          the waves, <i><span class="en">Od. 2.434</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 8.183</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
